<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-07-08T18:08:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-07-08T18:08:00-05:00" n="875" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d875">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">751G.00/7–854: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Department of
                                        State</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Embassy in
                                        France</gloss></hi><note n="1" xml:id="d875fn1">Drafted by
                                        <persName corresp="#p_TWR1">Tyler</persName> of <gloss target="#t_EUR1">EUR</gloss>/<gloss target="#t_WE1">WE</gloss>. Repeated to Geneva as <gloss target="#t_Tosec1">Tosec</gloss> 525, to Saigon as telegram 84, and to London
                                    as telegram 149.</note></head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi></seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1954-07-08T19:08:00-04:00">July 8, 1954—7:08
                                        p.m.</date></dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>84. Our willingness make public statement we will respect agreement
                                Indochina predicated assumption Associated States and in particular
                                Viet Nam would agree terms settlement.</p>
                            <p>We believe <persName corresp="#p_MFP1">Mendes-France</persName>
                                should be under no illusion that observance seven points (<gloss target="#t_Deptel1">Deptel</gloss> 4853<note n="2" xml:id="d875fn2">Dated June 28, <ref target="#pg_1256">p.
                                        1256</ref>.</note>) would of itself suffice without
                                agreement Associated States and request you make sure he understands
                                this.</p>
                            <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_DJF1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Dulles</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>